text: Bcycle, b-cycle, or variation, may refer to: * BCycle, public bikeshare subsidiary of Trek Bicycle, based in Waterloo, Wisconsin, USA; with bike programs spread across the U.S. * San Antonio B-Cycle, public bikeshare program in San Antonio, Texas, USA * Houston Bcycle, public bikeshare program operated by Houston Bike Share, in Houston, Texas, USA * Bicycle, a human- powered, two-wheeled vehicle, with front and aft wheels ==See also== * * * * * B (disambiguation) * Cycle (disambiguation) * Bicycle (disambiguation) * Bicyclic
title: Bcycle
